{"tid":347893,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【食物中毒】酷熱天氣下圍吃家鄉食品，5印傭屙嘔送院","createTime":"2017-08-05T08:33:20.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-05T09:31:56.000Z","uid":29314,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c2503d6761d825fa4c10afbeb41388eb193a3965","tid":347893,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:33:20.000Z","msg":"上周日下午在攝氏37度的酷熱天氣下，以百計外傭聚集美孚葵涌道天橋底邊談邊分享家鄉食品時，5名外傭疑食物中毒，部分人屙嘔不適，3人一度要躺在地上休息，其中1人更陷昏迷，救護員接報趕至為昏迷者急救及提供氧氣後，把5人送院治理。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170805/large/1501918323_a488.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170805%2Flarge%2F1501918323_a488.jpg&h=fd0108f0&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"76426cab70eef14d2534a830ef5115849dde73c1","tid":347893,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:34:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170805/large/1501918324_92ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170805%2Flarge%2F1501918324_92ab.jpg&h=55065aad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b74c6e44a144c18d9422be767031f988aa8b8655","tid":347893,"uid":22349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T08:39:13.000Z","msg":"天橋一浸腳臭味，d 外傭仲食得津津有味"},{"pid":"28a72cc96a82dc16bd199e6acb0cfc6dad80db8c","tid":347893,"uid":30040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:04:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daf5ea0a4a7ae59ae4e6c252d255c5227833bf21","tid":347893,"uid":54121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:11:16.000Z","msg":"睇到D相都覺臭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62ff0b0e9f6589c5d32e03c8166eb6a2ad443a21","tid":347893,"uid":62815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:12:26.000Z","msg":"逢禮拜六日經過天橋底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5f923f0d3bd87b1412df69e3e1ec801016dc584","tid":347893,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:12:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"788f5422a17cc07d4a6b692d5234e525dcbaf74a","tid":347893,"uid":51978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-05T09:31:56.000Z","msg":"不少美孚街坊及外傭均關注3名食物中毒印傭的情況，議論紛紛，有人懷疑是西瓜及汽水混合食用時引起中毒，但遭質疑欠醫學證明，亦有人關注是否含木薯製家鄉食品導致中毒，因木薯含毒素，若未煮便進食可能會食物中毒，另有街坊則關注會否是酷熱天氣令食物變壞。至日前更傳出有外傭送院後疑不治，令區內居民更為緊張，紛紛希望澄清事件真相。<br />\n<br />\n警方及消防處向《蘋果》證實， 7月30日下午2至3美孚曾發生懷疑食物中毒事故，當時5名女子(消息稱是5名介乎23至30歲的印傭)報稱不適送瑪嘉烈醫院。消息稱，5女子送院時有肚痛、嘔吐、屙嘔等食物中毒病徵，她們向醫護人員透露之前曾吃過一些自製家鄉食品，瑪嘉列醫院則回覆指5人送院時情況穩定，並於送院同日及翌日出院，故變相證實了「不治」一說純屬謠言。"}]}